text:
It's a lovely place. Everything was just perfect. We got a few friends over BBQ and it almost felt that I lived in Austin! Kitchen was stocked with herbs and spices, Nescafe Pods, all required utensils - what else can you ask?

Erica is pretty awesome - very responsive and helpful.

The place is in a great neighborhood - safe, quite, and very close to the lake.

When I'm back in Austin, I'd definitely come back here.
title: 3BR/2.5BA Tarrytown Duplex, Austin!
